{
  "text": "The INFORMS placebo group provides a selected \"natural history\" population of PPMS patients with \u22653 years of on-study assessment. The present analysis aimed to (1) describe differences between untreated PPMS patients with a stable, moderate, or severe clinical disease course as measured by EDSS, [CITATION_1] investigate the predictive value of normalized brain volume for clinical decline in untreated PPMS, and (3) investigate the relationship between previous and concurrent inflammatory lesion activity, brain volume loss, and clinical decline.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "32643307"
